Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,IN“The Flower Fairy”
Comment: 0,0:16:12.88,0:16:17.54,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}Wishing you were here
Comment: 0,0:16:18.90,0:16:25.01,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}When the whole world felt so clear
Comment: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:37.12,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}We said we would be together forever
Comment: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:42.31,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}What is done is done
Comment: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:49.45,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}You don’t have to please everyone
Comment: 0,0:16:49.94,0:16:55.33,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}Just be yourself
Comment: 0,0:16:55.95,0:17:05.74,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}And trust in your heart
Comment: 0,0:17:06.59,0:17:11.84,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}Now could be our time to shine
Comment: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:17.43,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}If you just take my hand
Comment: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:20.79,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}Over the sky
Comment: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:24.21,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}Spread our wings and fly
Comment: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:30.33,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}Not afraid, if we are not afraid to fall
Comment: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:33.53,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}Glowing inside
Comment: 0,0:17:33.53,0:17:36.54,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}Keep the dream alive
Comment: 0,0:17:36.54,0:17:38.15,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}Here with me
Comment: 0,0:17:38.15,0:17:42.71,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}Don’t you be afraid at all
Comment: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:52.03,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}Can you still see the enchanted kingdom
Comment: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:58.88,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}Where we danced with the flowers not caring the world
Comment: 0,0:17:58.88,0:18:05.71,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}When the fairies sang a sweet song to the heavens just for me and you
Comment: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:09.42,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}Can’t you feel it too
Comment: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:16.28,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}All the magic in you
Comment: 0,0:18:22.41,0:18:30.88,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}All the magic in you
Comment: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:47.29,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}All the magic in you
Comment: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:54.30,IN_EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}All the magic in you
Comment: 1,0:16:12.88,0:16:17.54,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}世界變得如此澄澈
Comment: 1,0:16:18.90,0:16:25.01,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}願你也能伴我左右
Comment: 1,0:16:25.01,0:16:37.12,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}我們曾立誓永不分離
Comment: 1,0:16:37.61,0:16:42.31,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}過去的事情已經過去
Comment: 1,0:16:43.57,0:16:49.45,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}你不必取悅任何人
Comment: 1,0:16:49.94,0:16:55.33,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}活出自己的模樣
Comment: 1,0:16:55.95,0:17:05.74,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}相信自己的心靈
Comment: 1,0:17:06.59,0:17:11.84,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}現在 屬於我們的閃耀時刻到了
Comment: 1,0:17:12.27,0:17:17.43,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}牽起我的手
Comment: 1,0:17:17.91,0:17:20.79,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}飛上藍天
Comment: 1,0:17:20.79,0:17:24.21,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}伸展翅膀 一同翱翔
Comment: 1,0:17:24.21,0:17:30.33,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}何必害怕跌落
Comment: 1,0:17:30.33,0:17:33.53,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}心中的光芒
Comment: 1,0:17:33.53,0:17:36.54,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}是夢想的火種
Comment: 1,0:17:36.54,0:17:38.15,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}與我一起
Comment: 1,0:17:38.15,0:17:42.71,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}甚麼都不必害怕
Comment: 1,0:17:46.30,0:17:52.03,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}你是否還能看見那魔法王國
Comment: 1,0:17:52.65,0:17:58.88,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}我們曾在那裡與花兒起舞 彷彿你我獨立於世界之外
Comment: 1,0:17:58.88,0:18:05.71,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}仙子們也為你我獻唱甜美的歌謠 歌聲直達雲端的天堂
Comment: 1,0:18:06.41,0:18:09.42,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}你是否還能感受到
Comment: 1,0:18:09.76,0:18:16.28,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}你心中的魔力
Comment: 1,0:18:22.41,0:18:30.88,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}你心中的魔力
Comment: 1,0:18:42.10,0:18:47.29,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}你心中的魔力
Comment: 1,0:18:48.32,0:18:54.30,IN_CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(480,720)\blur3\fax-0.1}你心中的魔力
